headline: Gilat's Q1 Earnings Ahead: Will Solid Deal Win Momentum Buoy Top Line?
summary: GILT's Q1 2025 performance is likely to have benefited from a surge in defense deals, momentum in its IFC business and steady gains from acquisition synergies.
